product.title: Cute Anime Melting Heart Hoodie
product.body_html:
• Description
  • FAQ
  • Shipping

  • A simple and cute design to share smiles with.

    This premium cute hoodie is designed with both comfort and cuteness in mind. Made with modern, cute, unique, and stylish design. The material is super soft, smooth, very comfortable to wear.


    This kawaii hoodie is available in seven different sizes for all to wear, measurements are shown below. 

      XS S M L XL XXL XXXL
    Chest (inches) 18 19 20 21 23 24 25
    Length (inches) 25 26 27 28 30 31 32
                   
      XS S M L XL XXL XXXL
    Chest          (cm) 46 49 52 55 58 61 64
    Length      (cm) 65 67 70 73 76 79 81


    Features

    🥰 Made from 50% premium polyester microfiber & 50% premium soft cotton
    😍 Promotes warmth, comfort, and durability



    All sizes:

    Measurements may be off by 1-5cm for rounding up to a whole number.

  • Please follow the washing labels when cleaning the garment:

     Max temperature 30c, or cold water. Reverse garment to protect the print.

     Do not bleach

     Dry by the sun or hang it to dry. 

     Dry cleaning

     

  • FREE Tracked Shipping to the United States, Canada, United Kingdom, Australia, New Zealand, Germany, Spain, France, Italy, Austria, Netherlands, and many more. Find out more here: Shipping Policy.

    Packaging time: 1-3 Business days

    Shipping time: Est 5-30 Business days
